import React from 'react';
import Form from 'react-bootstrap/Form';
import Col from 'react-bootstrap/Col';
import Button from 'react-bootstrap/Button';
import InfoCard from './InfoCard';
import { PlusSquare } from 'react-bootstrap-icons';
import styled from 'styled-components';


const ButtonText = styled.span`
    margin-left: 10px;
`

const SubmitButton = styled(Button)`
    display:flex;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 10px;
`

const Experiences = () => (
    <Form.Group controlId="experience">
        <InfoCard title={'Tidigare erfarenheter'}>
            <Form.Row>
                <Form.Group as={Col} controlId="title">
                    <Form.Label>Titel</Form.Label>
                    <Form.Control/>
                </Form.Group>

                <Form.Group as={Col} controlId="arbetsGivare">
                    <Form.Label>Arbetsgivare</Form.Label>
                    <Form.Control/>
                </Form.Group>
            </Form.Row>

            <Form.Row>
                <Form.Group as={Col} controlId="firstName">
                    <Form.Label>Start</Form.Label>
                    <Form.Control type="date" id="example-datepicker"/>
                </Form.Group>

                <Form.Group as={Col} controlId="lastName">
                    <Form.Label>Slut</Form.Label>
                    <Form.Control type="date" id="example-datepicker"/>
                </Form.Group>
            </Form.Row>

            <Form.Row>
                <Form.Group as={Col} controlId="title">
                    <Form.Label>Titel</Form.Label>
                    <Form.Control placeholder="Lärare"/>
                </Form.Group>

                <Form.Group as={Col} controlId="phone">
                    <Form.Label>Telefonnummer</Form.Label>
                    <Form.Control placeholder="+46760042332"/>
                </Form.Group>
            </Form.Row>
            <Form.Group controlId="exampleForm.ControlTextarea1">
                <Form.Label>Beskrivning</Form.Label>
                <Form.Control as="textarea" rows="3" />
            </Form.Group>
        </InfoCard>
        <SubmitButton variant="primary" type="submit">
            <PlusSquare/>
            <ButtonText>Lägg till erfarenhet</ButtonText>
        </SubmitButton>
    </Form.Group> 
)



export default Experiences
